<td style=" color:#000000; font-size:12pt; background-color:#FFFFFF; font-family:arial; bLabel:main; bEditID:r3st1;" tEditID="c1r1" locked="0" aEditID="c1r1" >
<![CDATA[<div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: right;"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-family: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif; "><font class="Apple-style-span" size="6" color="#000066">{!Contact.SchoolText__c}</font></span></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: right;"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="'Times New Roman', Times, serif" size="4" color="#ff6600"><i>Chartered By The British Schools Foundation</i></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: right;"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif" size="6" color="#c0c0c0"><b><i><br></i></b></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: right;"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="'Times New Roman', Times, serif" size="1" color="#ff6600"><i><br></i></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: left;"><div style="font-family: Times; font-size: medium;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif">24th April 2015</font></div></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: left;"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="-webkit-border-horizontal-spacing: 5px; -webkit-border-vertical-spacing: 5px; "><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></span></font></div><div style="text-align: left;"><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="border-spacing: 5px;">Dear&nbsp;{!Contact.Salutation}&nbsp;{!Contact.FirstName}&nbsp;{!Contact.LastName}</span></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><br></div><div><div><div style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif">A small but significant number of Year 7 pupils have misused their school laptops and other personal devices to receive and send on indecent images to other pupils. Today Ms Coates and I spoke to all of Year 7: although the majority are not involved in this situation, I felt it important that all the year group received a transparent message. I made it clear that any pupil misusing computers in this way would not be welcome in our school. I also briefly discussed the dangers to them, and the legal implications of them becoming involved in this sort of communication. We have dealt robustly with those pupils who instigated this event.</font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Appropriate use of technology is a subject that is scheduled into our PSHE calendar for later this term, and there will be ample opportunity for mature discussion of this topic. In the meantime I have told pupils to inform a member of staff immediately if they receive any communication they feel may compromise them. Similarly I have told them to remove themselves from any 'chat groups' where inappropriate language has been used.</font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Although I cannot guarantee that nothing like this will happen again, I am confident that Year 7 will respond to this advice, and that sound educational awareness of these issues, and sensitive yet meaningful discussion will help to keep your children safe.&nbsp;</font></div></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><br></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Kind regards</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Derek Mackey</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Head of Secondary</font></div></div></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><br></div></div></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: left;"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif">{!Contact.SchoolText__c}</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: left;"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><i><font class="Apple-style-span" color="#ff6600"><b>World Class Education</b></font></i></span></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: left;"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: left;"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif">__________________________________________________________</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: center;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="1">{!User.School_List_Email_Footer__c}</font><font class="Apple-style-span" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;" face="Arial, sans-serif" size="1">&nbsp;</font></div>]]></td>
